  <brief_title>TRENDY Follow-up: Study on Endothelial Function in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Study on Endothelial Function in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
